  2. ./keys/<iso_stem>.key   (local cache, alternate ext)
  3. Scrape https://ps3.aldostools.org/dkey.html (stdlib only) → save to ./keys/

Binary lookup order:
  1. Current working directory
  2. /userdata/roms/ps3/
  3. System PATH

Usage: python3 ps3-decrypt [iso_directory]
